SELECT 
            SUM(
                CASE 
                    WHEN end_time IS NOT NULL THEN (strftime('%s', end_time) - strftime('%s', start_time))
                    ELSE (strftime('%s', last_heartbeat) - strftime('%s', start_time))
                END
            ) AS "total_seconds!: i64"
        FROM sessions
        WHERE project_id = ?
        AND session_type = 'FOCUS'
        AND is_deleted = 0
